by Ghost (JustAJuxtaposition)

She wished she’d never wandered off or touched that which she should never have touched. But Theodora cannot keep dwelling on the events of the past because she is the daughter of Tony Stark, and their life is all about moving forward. When Pepper Potts inherits the seat at Stark Industries, Theodora becomes acquainted with an eloquent newcomer, and what she knows and has to tell Theodora of herself changes her life forever. Her only hope of keeping any sort of normality in her life or so she is told is to work together with a remarkable group of people.
